# Title: Scripted Diagnostics Turn Off Check Enabled - Registry
# Author: Christopher Peacock @securepeacock, SCYTHE @scythe_io
# Date: 2022-06-15
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects enabling TurnOffCheck which can be used to bypass defense of MSDT Follina vulnerability
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_enabling_turnoffcheck.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Administrator actions

Details="DWORD (0x00000001)" TargetObject="*\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Windows\\ScriptedDiagnostics\\TurnOffCheck"